Meet the Author



William T. Monahan has held a number of top positions with 3M and became Chairman and Chief Executive of Imation when the units comprising it were spun off, some only marginally profitable and others losing money. Monahan transformed them into a profitable, successful business. From 1999 to 2004, Imation's stock price increased by 120%, an average annual return of 18%.










